{"tid":277493,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Heath Ledger既Joker真係好撚痴線","createTime":"2017-06-09T15:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T15:48:36.000Z","uid":115607,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f107edae15469a437c9a6dbc1bfe85c5ea935262","tid":277493,"uid":115607,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:37:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u8PxG5zvgOM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Du8PxG5zvgOM&d=BpN9fCDnh%2FVsk4kBd7LYQGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ba77fdaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u8PxG5zvgOM</a><br />\n笑聲 表情 小動作活演小丑呢個角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全表達到Joker既瘋狂 <br />\n<br />\nLeto既Joker完全比唔上 不過佢既造型係適合Suicide Squad既風格多d<br />\n<br />\n可能套戲cut得太多 令Leto表現唔到 <br />\n<br />\nLeto既Joker既設定無咁吸引 似係一個鍾意錢既黑社會大佬多d<br />\n<br />\n而Ledger既Joker純粹係想表達人性醜惡 身邊既野根本唔重要<br />\n<br />\n可惜入戲太深 死得太早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係第三集就可以欣賞佢演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b8a12134b575a9bc9c08aa11673e1459da4df0","tid":277493,"uid":93986,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"完全演出了新一代新風格的joker<br />\n前無古人 後無來者。<br />\n一代經典人物"},{"pid":"2b277cef9db291d1db3371bf40330800c837800b","tid":277493,"uid":55851,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"Leto用手背個紋身扮笑果吓我一世都記得，On9到打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06be36997f74a8ab4015f4618b6eab8bf24af27","tid":277493,"uid":115607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"其實1989既小丑有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解咁多人讚佢演得好"},{"pid":"4bc7cfac633754898177548c76248be786139756","tid":277493,"uid":58610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy